Image(painter = painter, contentDescription = null)

‚ö†Ô∏è Mistake: Launching multiple coroutines without proper error isolation. If one fails, all others get cancelled.

‚úÖ Use `supervisorScope` to isolate them:

viewModelScope.launch {
    supervisorScope {
        launch { fetchData1() }
        launch { fetchData2() }
    }
}

