}

// In test:
onNodeWithTag("submit_button").assertIsDisplayed()

‚úÖ Use `debounce` operator on a `Flow`:

val queryFlow = MutableStateFlow("")

LaunchedEffect(Unit) {
    queryFlow
        .debounce(300)
        .distinctUntilChanged()
        .collect { viewModel.search(it) }
}

‚ö†Ô∏è This collect runs on a non-lifecycle-aware scope.

‚úÖ Use `collectAsState()` or lifecycle-aware collectors:

lifecycleScope.launch {
    repeatOnLifecycle(Lifecycle.State.STARTED) {
