LaunchedEffect(Unit) {
    val data = fetchData()
    loading.value = false
}

answerCode:
‚úÖ If `fetchData()` throws an exception, `loading.value = false` is never reached.

üí° Use `try-finally`:

LaunchedEffect(Unit) {
    try {
        fetchData()
    } finally {
        loading.value = false
    }
}

